prompt: An isolated UI button element on transparent background in the style of JRR Tolkien Father Christmas illustrations, detailed watercolor and pen-and-ink on aged parchment. A long horizontal rectangular button with textured aged leather appearance in warm dark brown tones. Warm magical golden glow around the button. Medieval handcrafted aesthetic, fine crosshatching details, sepia tones, storybook illustration style.
